{"tid":471186,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門立會研中止蘇嘉豪職務","createTime":"2017-11-17T04:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T05:26:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ed8508918997abf503b8a717a3daeada412ba6bf","tid":471186,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:23:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171117/20216859\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171117%2F20216859&d=j3GOyvcuxBwnVifK%2BrcsgJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=f7eb1c79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171117%2F20216859&h=bb422f4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171117/20216859</a><br />\n<br />\n澳門立會研中止蘇嘉豪職務<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171117/large/17la5p4new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171117%2Flarge%2F17la5p4new.jpg&h=eb5b4618&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】澳門民主派立法會議員蘇嘉豪（圖）涉去年5月在澳門特首官邸外非法集會，被控加重違令罪，澳門立法會章程及任期委員會昨召開會議，討論法官要求立法會中止蘇的議員職務，蘇及另一民主派議員高天賜有列席會議。該委員會決定不會就是否中止蘇的議員職務作傾向性意見，交由立法會大會以不記名方式表決。<br />\n<br />\n林玉鳳：我傾向寬鬆處理<br />\n<br />\n委員會主席高開賢會後表示，今次是澳門回歸後首次處理有關議題，會內主要討論相關程序，並無討論案件細節或議員行為，委員會決定不會就是否中止蘇的議員職務作傾向性意見，只會論述中止議員職務對議員及立法會的影響，並交由立法會大會根據議事規則，以不記名方式表決。委員會下周一再開會，冀完成意見書及提交立法會主席賀一誠。被問及賀要求法庭延遲審訊，以等候立法會作出表決，高開賢指沒收到相關消息。<br />\n<br />\n蘇嘉豪會後形容會議討論過程開放，他在會上獲准就事件陳述意見，他質疑為何立法會議員需中止職務才可接受法庭聆訊，強調今次是為公民利益及行使公民權利而引發的事件，他並無濫用議員職權貪污瀆職。<br />\n<br />\n澳門立法會議員林玉鳳稱，蘇今次涉及的控罪行為與議員職務無關，她認為毋須中止蘇的議員職務，「我傾向寬鬆處理」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者謝明明"},{"pid":"1fd8ae4d4226ff0a59c2f000e9aa9fec2aca321d","tid":471186,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:25:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有樣學樣玩Dq</span>"},{"pid":"432db9e69742090d2775c61bcffacdb7a3cdd4da","tid":471186,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:29:25.000Z","msg":"澳門真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da366db120bb9412b78994f3a2b0ea1167f8365d","tid":471186,"uid":1009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:53:57.000Z","msg":"根據黃絲熱狗邏輯，蘇嘉豪係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade4c4edcbd328084df458aa20a267c4e58d7a38","tid":471186,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T05:02:25.000Z","msg":"你澳門得4席係泛民,玩條毛咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f654381212797b8cd943a9402f6a0722cb90c762","tid":471186,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"好慘，咁就d 了"},{"pid":"945b6637b3cf7449ec6645e4e419923c68a02dd9","tid":471186,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T05:18:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4e1df52a3eeaa2eb58302ff3c6150442c9e3ac5","tid":471186,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T05:26:25.000Z","msg":"乜澳門有民主派架咩?<br />\n肯定係鬼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}